	<h1 class="title">阿里巴巴、腾讯、百度，要一起把《小门神》卖出个好价钱</h1>
	<div class="author-date clearfix">					
			<div class="author clearfix">
					<span class="avatar x25 circle">
						<img src="/system/users/faces/73/small/73.jpg?1415670876" alt="">
					</span>
				<span class="name">俞斯译 </span>
			</div>
		<span class="date smart-date" data-originDate="2015-09-23 20:02:26 +0800"></span>
	</div>
	<div class="banner">
			<img src="/system/articles/articleshows/15449/medium/15449.jpg?1443008906" alt="" />			
	</div>
